ing: 3 cooked, boneless chicken breast halves, shredded
1 (4 ounce) can chopped green chile peppers
des: "Simple seasoned chicken and stewed tomatoes soup with spicy taste.  Colorful.  Sprinkle shredded Jack cheese on top of each serving.  Add tortilla chips on each serving plate with soup."
ins: Place cooked chicken, kidney beans, corn, tomatoes, onion, red and green bell peppers, chiles, broth and cumin in a large pot over medium heat.  Simmer 45 minutes.
